test_even_range:
assert [4, 6, 8, 10, 12, 14, ...] == []
  Left contains 7 more items, first extra item: 4
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [4, 6, 8, 10, 12, 14, 16]
test_large_range:
assert [2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, ...] == []
  Left contains 7 more items, first extra item: 2
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8]
